10:36.385 --> 10:38.262
-Uh, I can't tell you that.

10:38.346 --> 10:41.599
All right.  You'd have to kill me.

10:42.725 --> 10:44.935
-Currently eight.

10:45.019 --> 10:48.147
Stay out of Brooklyn.
