10:49.398 --> 10:52.151
Wow, look at that.
I'm starting to believe the hype.

10:52.777 --> 10:55.404
<i></i>
<i>-I think we'll make the white clam.</i>

10:55.488 --> 10:57.657
<i>I've been hearing</i>
<i>so much about this pie.</i>

