to get back here.

11:02.578 --> 11:04.955
There was a guy in the alleyway,
he used to cut clams on the half-shell,

11:05.039 --> 11:06.749
called Nick, he was a bookie.

11:06.832 --> 11:10.211
He came in, he goes, "Do you ever think
of putting them on a pizza?"

11:10.294 --> 11:11.337
Really?

11:11.420 --> 11:13.381
Put them on the pizza
