11:13.464 --> 11:16.509
All right.
You put a lot of clams on the pie.

11:16.592 --> 11:18.386
No, it's about normal.

11:18.469 --> 11:21.514
A little oregano,
grated cheese, fresh garlic.

11:21.597 --> 11:23.015
And that's it?
-That's it.

11:23.099 --> 11:24.975
Stand back.
-Yeah.

11:25.976 --> 11:27.812
